summary: Merged Binance WebSocket + technical indicators (HEAD) with Polymarket API client (main). All features from both branches preserved and integrated.
strategyUsed: preserve-both-features: HEAD added Binance WebSocket streaming with RSI/MACD technical indicators, while origin/main added comprehensive Polymarket API client for market discovery. Both implementations are complementary and work together for the trading bot, so all features were preserved and integrated into unified market_data module.
